      <div id="bottom_left_words", class="words">
        This way, you can see Suchaaver's illustrations, concept art, graphic design, and thoughts on various topics.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class = "small-3 small-offset-2 columns">
      <div id="bottom_right_words", class="words">
        Over here, you can follow Joraaver in his various interests, from robotics and the Arduino, to juggling and fitness.
